### Key Technical Notes — Next.js 16

- `proxy.ts` not `middleware.ts` — export named `proxy`
- `cookies()` must be awaited — done in server.ts
- `params` is async — handled in all dynamic routes
- Supabase relations return arrays for one-to-many, objects for many-to-one via FK hint
- FK hint syntax: `table!constraint_name(columns)` — no spaces inside parens

